<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1010713-why-would-i-bother-to-read-the-book-when">Why. would I bother to read the book when the reviews have already told the story?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1010713'><a id="like_count_community_question_1010713" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1010713?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">31 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F30687200-the-stranger-in-the-woods">like</a></span>

</li>
