<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer12698670585015788977">Michael Finkel is the author of &quot;The Stranger in the Woods&quot; and &quot;True Story,&quot; which was adapted into a 2015 motion picture. He has reported from more than 50 countries and written for National Geographic, GQ, Rolling Stone, Esquire, Vanity Fair, The Atlantic, and The New York Times Magazine. He lives with his family in northern Utah and southern France.</span>
  <span id="freeText12698670585015788977" style="display:none">Michael Finkel is the author of "The Stranger in the Woods" and "True Story," which was adapted into a 2015 motion picture. He has reported from more than 50 countries and written for National Geographic, GQ, Rolling Stone, Esquire, Vanity Fair, The Atlantic, and The New York Times Magazine. He lives with his family in northern Utah and southern France.</span>
